INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (141, 'Hi. The symptoms of an STI differ in men and women.  We use symptoms to identify the cause of the STI and tests to confirm. Generally, we test fluids from the genital organs to identify an STI. 
In men, 
*urethral swabs are taken from within the tip of the penis; 
*discharge of the penis can be tested as well.
Sometimes the *urine may be tested for STI like Clamydia, and *blood tests can identify HIV (as well as *mouth swabs).  
(For homosexuals, swabs from the anus may be used). 
In women,
Pelvic tests - taking swabs from the *vagina and inner lining of the *womb are used.', 70, 63, 0, null, 0, '2018-10-14 12:21:17', '2019-07-07 16:48:50', null);
