Are you in a sound state of mind? Are you depressed? Are you anxious and over worrying? Especially with young men, this could influence your erections. Having a relaxed and worry free mind can improve this condition.

If this tends to occur during intercourse, are you indulging in foreplay with your partner? Taking it slow allows for the urge to heighten and the blood flow to the penis to increase. Enjoy the process of intercourse and don’t rush it. Talk with your partner if there are any insecurities. This can boost the attraction between you two and make the process enjoyable.

