INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (762, 'Hi, 

You have stated just a dosage and no name of the pill, however, I will go ahead and assume it is a particular pill because of the reason it was taken. This pill you might have taken is a very dangerous drug to take without a health worker’s supervision. 
This is a prescription drug and without a prescription you COULD have also purchase a substandard drug. 

However, let’s assume you took the right pill and of good quality, the best way to confirm loss of pregnancy after an abortive attempt is to do a repeat pregnancy test in 4 weeks, only then can you confirm a pregnancy loss. Ultrasound scans on the other hand can reveal presence or absence earlier.  

