INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (906, 'Hello, 

Trimethylaminuria is a metabolic disorder cause by the inability of the body to break down trimethylamine. 
Trimethylamine has a fishy odor and is produced in the intestines when certain types of food (i.e. eggs, liver, legumes, fish and some vegetables) are digested. When it can’t be broken down, this leads to an accumulation in the body causing it to be excreted via the sweat, urine, and breath, giving them  a characteristic fishy odor of trimethylaminuria.

An attempt at diagnosis usually starts with the presence of characteristic signs and symptoms, followed by urine test (to check the amount of trimethylamine in the urine) and genetic testing which are used to confirm the diagnosis.

I advise you speak to your physician who will refer you for the needed investigation and to the appropriate specialist, if required. If you would like us to help you with one, please contact us via the Contact Us tab in the menu.', 13, 479, 0, null, 0, '2019-08-31 05:57:14', '2019-08-31 05:57:14', null);
INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (907, 'Hello,

A blighted ovum is what occurs when an implanted fertilised egg in the uterus fails to develop into an embryo. What this means is that, although there’s a positive pregnancy test, and other parts of the egg may have formed, the gestational sac remains empty. 

Unfortunately, there’s no growing baby.

The hormone that signals pregnancy is still usually being released, and this can be read during pregnancy as a viable pregnancy, however, an obstetric scan will reveal the true status of the pregnancy. 

I’m sorry to inform you that a blighted ovum eventually leads to a miscarriage, and it is not able to turn into a viable pregnancy.

My advise is to have a repeat scan at a reputable centre and speak to a gynaecologist on how to proceed. 

I wish you all the best', 13, 484, 0, null, 0, '2019-08-31 06:10:28', '2019-08-31 06:10:28', null);
