INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (1140, 'Hi, 

First, Libido is a person''s overall sexual drive or desire for sexual activity. 
Do you have a low libido or you can’t maintain an erection? 
Please note that CIALIS does not increase a man''s sexual desire, sex drive or libido. It helps increase blood flow to the penis and can help men with erectile dysfunction get and keep an erection for sexual activity when sexually stimulated. It does not induce erections in the absence of sexual stimulation.

Cialis is a prescription drug and must be prescribed by a doctor after examining you. It is not appropriate or safe for everyone to take it, as certain health conditions and other medicines can make it unsafe to take Cialis.

