It is important that you maintain healthier lifestyle choices, improve your diet and eat healthier, get regular exercise and enough sleep, cut down on the alcohol, and reduce stress.', 13, 634, 0, null, 0, '2019-10-13 07:36:25', '2019-10-13 07:36:25', null);
INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (1141, 'Hello, 

