INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (2105, 'Hello,
Sorry to hear about your other eye but thankful we have 2 eyes and the other works perfectly.

However, because you’re using one eye doesn’t mean you would develop eye diseases earlier but it is important to Care for our eyes like we do our bodies. 

There are a number of fruits/foods that help protect the eyes, but look out for those high in Vitamin A. Carrots, Kale, Spinach, Tomatoes, Eggs, Tangerines etc. 
