INSERT INTO ebdb.thread_comments (id, content, user_id, thread_id, is_retrieved, retrieved_at, is_answer, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES (2349, 'Hello, 

The rib cage consists of 24 ribs, 12 on either side, shielding the vital organs of the chest, including the heart and the lungs, from damage. Not sure which rib in particular you are referring to. 

